{"tid":2375835,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"河南省村民慶祝聖誕節 被宗教局重罰16萬","createTime":"2021-01-22T10:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T03:31:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"49ec1171850337b4929c59c5540cde2311e73ef0","tid":2375835,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G_lcXODBMmmrieVQ_IoYxUYoKQk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4P5OD6F4LRBGNFZF4D3DCCYRJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG_lcXODBMmmrieVQ_IoYxUYoKQk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4P5OD6F4LRBGNFZF4D3DCCYRJE.jpg&h=827c12fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n維權網周四（21日）報道指，河南省魯山縣張良鎮黃莊村基督徒牛國寶因為慶祝聖誕節，遭當地民族宗教事務局開出16萬元人民幣（下同，約19.1萬港元）行政處罰罰單。<br />\n<br />\n據指，牛國寶等40多名基督徒去年12月19日聚會，預祝聖誕節，其間魯山縣宗教局人員闖入會場，不許基督徒慶祝，並沒收基督教書籍、春聯、掛曆等物品，登記參加聚會的基督徒。<br />\n<br />\n事隔一個月後，魯山縣宗教局於本月19日，向組織聖誕聚會的牛國寶開出16萬元罰單，指是依《宗教事務條例》第71條「為違法宗教活動提供條件的，由宗教事務部門給予警告，有違法所得、非法財物的，沒收違法所得和非法財物，情節嚴重的，並處2萬元以上20萬元以下的罰款；有違法房屋、構築物的，由規劃、建設等部門依法處理；有違反治安管理行為的，依法給予治安管理處罰。」魯山縣宗教局限牛國寶3日內提出聽證申請，逾期則視為放棄聽證權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210122/VXVXW7VJVFHVDEIRV5MELIQQYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210122%2FVXVXW7VJVFHVDEIRV5MELIQQYY%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TTUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=9836d2b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210122%2FVXVXW7VJVFHVDEIRV5MELIQQYY%2F&h=371868ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210122/VXVXW7VJVFHVDEIRV5MELIQQYY/</a>"},{"pid":"d25d7d43ea9b19ccae678144edb419099ce16e00","tid":2375835,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20c0c080c29386237d6851e91df61c544f5c55d","tid":2375835,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"教宗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540ce8fb9a3bdc8168198107efa46a265f2f2aea","tid":2375835,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c6eb49678c793bdb03aae36a1274cffdbcedc4","tid":2375835,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b20c0c080c29386237d6851e91df61c544f5c55d","tid":2375835,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"教宗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"無所謂，收多d奉獻咪得lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cad938545c895013d592c464df549b3b84aa753","tid":2375835,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb53c6fd3fe8aa3af2b285d13013f9a9c1d248d","tid":2375835,"uid":383344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"已知河南人均月入及參與慶祝人數，求還清罰款所需時間"},{"pid":"20efe115b00526ba64bcf137564fc796045a2cda","tid":2375835,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:43:26.000Z","msg":"中國係冇聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf4f88921d46dbdbcfa48595d409b09c6abe0d2","tid":2375835,"uid":192732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbb53c6fd3fe8aa3af2b285d13013f9a9c1d248d","tid":2375835,"uid":383344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"已知河南人均月入及參與慶祝人數，求還清罰款所需時間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:1